| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2843 — Recovery Inhibition (beast)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9a2d0daf-3f94-52dd-8bc5-809197e82b04"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
